  <brief_title>Metabolic and Cardiovascular Effects of Dipeptidyl Peptidase-4 (DPP-4) or Sodium-glucose Co-transporter Type 2 (SGLT2) Inhibitors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of the DPP-4 or SGLT2 Inhibitors on the Metabolic Cardiovascular Systems in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Kurume University</agency>
